quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,44,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko jii…ďu-jaa…ďu koy…ói ! min ngonaani anndu…ďe firo koy…ói !"."
  12,45,"Da…ónoo…óo on e …ďeya …ói…óo miijitii …ďaawo dumunna o wi'i: "Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee kam"."
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo gooŇč…óu…óo! haalani min fii na'i jee…ói…ói pay…ói, na √Īaama poo∆īu…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e butaali jee…ói…ói kecci e go…ó…ói jooru…ói, mbelejo'o mi ruttoo ka yim…ďe …ďen, belejo'o, …ďe ngannday"."
  12,47,"O maaki: "On ndemat duu…ói jee…ói…ói jokkondir…ói. Kala ko co√Ī…óon, ngccon …óum ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa see…óa e kon ko √Īaamoton"."
  12,48,"Refti aroyat …ďaawo …óum, duu…ďi jee…ói…ói ca…ótu…ói, …óin (duu…ďi) no √Īaama …óuum ko marna…óon …ói si wonaa see…óa e ko maroton [fii awdi]."
  12,49,"Refti aroya …ďaawo …óuum, hitaande, ko e mayre yim…ďe …ďen to…ďetee, ko e mayre kadi …ďe kamata."
  12,50,"Laam…óo on wi'i: "ngaddanee kam on". Nde imminaa…óo on arunoo mo, o maaki: "Rutto ka koohoojo maa on la…ďndo…óaa mo: Ko woni fiyaaku …ďen rew…ďe ta∆īnoo…ďe juu…óe mun …óen? Pellet Joomi am ko ganndu…óo pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen"."
  12,51,"[Laam…óo on] wi'i: "Ko hol…óum wonnoo fiyaaku mon tuma …óa…ď…ďirno…óon Yuusufa hoore-makko?" ∆Āe mbi'i: "Moolaare Alla! min nganndiraa mo ko boni". ∆Āeyngu laam…óo on wi'i: "Jooni goonga kan fee√Īii. Ko min …óa…ď…ďirnoo mo hoore-makko, pellet ko o jeyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen"."
  12,52,""∆äuum ko fii yo o anndu won¬īde mi jamfaaki mo ka wirnii, e won¬īde Alla fewnatah pewje jamfotoo…ďe …ďen."